org.vertx.java.core.spi.cluster

Interface AsyncMultiMap<K,V>


  • public interface AsyncMultiMap<K,V>
    An asynchronous multi-map. A multi-map holds a List of values against each key as opposed to a single value, as with a Map. The cluster implementation should ensure that any entries placed in the map from any node are available on any node of the cluster.
